{"tid":280280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭家富伙拍港獨派陳國強區議員　疑參與新東補選","createTime":"2017-06-12T03:28:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-19T09:33:44.000Z","uid":96964,"like":4,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6147e8bbc0221f29b1a9200d34e1d59d2467f186","tid":280280,"uid":96964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:28:00.000Z","msg":"以「民主派律師」作名銜的鄭家富，與6名沙田區議員丘文俊、趙柱幫、陳兆陽、許銳宇、<span style=\"color: red;\">陳國強</span>、黎梓恩共同製作橫額掛於街上，宣傳「連結世代 實踐革新」。翻查資料，丘文俊、趙柱幫、陳兆陽、許銳宇本身是新民主同盟成員，其中丘文俊、趙柱幫、陳兆陽在去年立法會選舉中為鄭家富站台，並在選舉後退黨；許銳宇之後亦退黨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497078990841\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497078990841&d=mxKMgU3sJiIz7Hst0GZ%2BFdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=214aa703\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170610%2Fs00001%2F1497078990841&h=a5a05c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170610/s00001/1497078990841</a>"},{"pid":"48d6dc609284c7ea7b4041ce603bcc18727bdda0","tid":280280,"uid":85819,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T03:30:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7870aaebb040a5dc7e3cd7c3bc6cd66c8101cb0a","tid":280280,"uid":3241,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T04:54:15.000Z","msg":"又黎重演廢陶同鳩達攬炒<br />\n<br />\n歷史不停地重演<br />\n我代阿頂下面排緊隊隻豬講聲多謝"},{"pid":"e10617b998ce46e3cf15dbcfe53a24d070cf225f","tid":280280,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"good"},{"pid":"563480e83b908682762625933d914ac905a9545a","tid":280280,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T05:47:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鄭家富好過X國威</blockquote><br />\n咁快失憶"},{"pid":"3631fe0991fff07eaa5400edd8a3da9a05ad5aa0","tid"